--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> ::Starlight::
> 
> Starlight smiles and gains altitude, easily avoiding Teltoli. She 
> fires two more stinger missiles and four darts down at the Maximal.

Teltoli:

She flaps her wings to rise her altitude as well, sheathing her whip 
and pulling out her rapier, flinging it at close range at Starlight, 
straight for her chest. After dodging the two stinger missiles, she 
gets hit in the wing by two of the dart. Teltoli growls and yanks 
them out, waiting to see if her sword hit Starlight.
